dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Ralph White. May I have your name, please?
Hello Ralph, my name is Jacqueline Howard.
Thank you, Jacqueline. How can I assist you today?
I need to inquire about my premium payment. I missed last month's payment.
I can assist with that. Can you please provide me with your policy number and the amount of the missed premium payment?
My policy number is two three four five six and the missed payment amount is two zero zero.
Thank you for providing the information, Jacqueline. Let me look into your payment history. Please hold on for a moment.
I found the missed payment in our records. You can make the payment online or over the phone. Would you like me to guide you through the process?
Yes, please guide me through the online payment process.
Sure, I will walk you through the steps. Thank you for your patience, Jacqueline. Your payment will be processed shortly. Is there anything else I can help you with today?
Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance, Jacqueline. Have a great day!
